794.mp4?t=1729764301\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147040/extras/e31a9458c639a3cda4cbbe3179a01b97.avif?t=1729764301\" width=800 height=77 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >坐下来欣赏表演！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您的策略选择将在战斗中自动展现，物品组合将自动发挥作用。观看您的构建如何对抗对手！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147040/extras/5365946d81bfd68538e3e94f2439e100.poster.avif?t=1729764301\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147040/extras/5365946d81bfd68538e3e94f2439e100.webm?t=1729764301\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147040/extras/5365946d81bfd68538e3e94f2439e100.mp4?t=1729764301\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
